CreditSudhaar is an online finance and credit platform for consumers in India. Established in 2010 CreditSudhaar currently has a client base in 217 cities.
CreditSudhaar offers credit and financial tools including free credit scores, credit monitoring, credit score simulators to its clients. CreditSudhaar also provides customers with a wide range of analytical assessments to the users helping them to have an in-depth understanding on their credit status. The Credit simulator helps the user to check the impact of various credit actions on their credit health. Headquartered in Mumbai, CreditSudhaar has offices in Delhi and Bangalore and has an employee strength of 150 people.
